snippet.textDisplay: Honestly I think T3 is a better movie. Sure it's goofy at times but Nick Stahl's portrayal of John as a man without a purpose, slowly realising that he can't run away from destiny is pretty good, the bit where the psychiatrist from the previous films sees the T-800 in the cemetery and runs is hilarious, the action scenes in general are pretty good and the ending is amazing, arguably the best ending of the entire franchise.
